"},"$:/plugins/mabuqian/xnote/overview/en/changelog":{"title":"$:/plugins/mabuqian/xnote/overview/en/changelog","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"! 0.3.0

2025-01-10

A short mode has been added to save space.

! 0.2.0

Added a right sidebar. At the same time, both the top bar and the right sidebar can be chosen whether to display. However, it is advisable to keep only one. Because without the page button, using TiddlyWiki can be very troublesome.


! 0.1.0

The top search box has been removed, leaving only the page button. Meanwhile, the sidebar has also removed the main title and subtitle, replacing them with a simple search box. The sidebar allows the selection of different styles.

The settings style has been modified.
"},"$:/plugins/mabuqian/xnote/overview/en/readme":{"title":"$:/plugins/mabuqian/xnote/overview/en/readme","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"This plugin is mainly modified from the [[notebook|https://saqimtiaz.github.io/sq-tw/notebook.html]] theme plugin. Since the original plugin has not been maintained for many years, and I have made some special modifications to it, I am releasing it under a new plugin name.

This plugin does not currently support mobile devices, and there may be some issues.

Code: https://github.com/dongrentianyu/sin/

Site: https://dongrentianyu.github.io/sin/

